reviewText: Good item but was damaged because packaging
Glad I got this collection. Family loves it big time!!!
I've wanted something like this for years and they definitely delivered. The extras are alright, I'm mainly happy to have the series all in one collection.

A little pricey but anime always has been. This is a great anime starts off light hearted, but well...no spoilers you'll soon find out. I'd say good for kids 16+ although no nudity, there is sexual situations and violence
